headline: 2 No-Brainer Stocks to Buy Now With $250 Before They Soar in 2025, According to Wall Street
summary: Among the 47 analysts who follow Datadog, the median target price is $160 per share.  Among the 40 analysts who follow The Trade Desk, the median target price is $142 per share.  Importantly, Datadog and The Trade Desk suffered large drawdowns following their latest financial reports, but that creates an opportunity.
